            <section>
               <id root="c3078119-b9ce-4615-ac1f-01658525bbe9"/>
               <code code="42229-5" codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" displayName="SPL UNCLASSIFIED SECTION"/>
               <title>INGREDIENTS</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>Each gram of 20% benzocaine gel contains between 180-220 mg benzocaine U.S.P., in a water soluble base of PEG 3350 U.S.P., PEG 400 U.S.P., flavor, sodium saccharin U.S.P., and FD&amp;C Red #40.</paragraph>
               </text>
               <effectiveTime value="20100513"/>
            </section>
         </component>
         <component>
